<subSubSection id="59F8CF5F4BFC6F8451C91ACEC50213AD" pageId="0" pageNumber="123" type="etymology">
<paragraph id="EF361C54F142FC5B14AA9E479198E83E" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">Etymology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4D5BAF49887E768B6DF618CC109BB69F" pageId="0" pageNumber="123">The specific patronymic epithet is dedicated to Dr Wen-I Chou (Taiwan, China), the collector of the holotype.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
